{"type": "article", "id": 47304, "title": "秋千摇椅不罕见，不过这个特别简洁｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-11-16T23:26:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 2383, "name": "书架"}, {"id": 7158, "name": "壁灯"}, {"id": 6292, "name": "挂钟"}, {"id": 45565, "name": "Malagana Design"}, {"id": 45566, "name": "Internoitaliano"}, {"id": 45567, "name": "Super Local"}, {"id": 45568, "name": "Astro"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 12, "praise_count": 204, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171116203211VJWEDgKu87XACwGT.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「<b>BestDesign</b>」或是「<b>Qthings</b>」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Samaná project by José Bermúdez,  Vrokka &amp; Fango Studio</h3><p>墨西哥设计师 <a href=\"http://jose-bermudez.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">José Bermúdez</a> 和哥伦比亚设计师 <a href=\"http://www.vrokka.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vrokka</a> 以及 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/fangostudio/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fango Studio</a> 合力开发的项目名为 Samaná，希望能够促进中南美洲咖啡文化的和谐。整个项目包括一个可以作为桌子的橱柜、咖啡杯、咖啡勺和一个小容器。橱柜的四个弧形角坐于细长的黑色金属框架上，顶部打开后，所有制作咖啡的器具和材料都可以收纳其中，关闭时就可以当作咖啡桌使用。</p><p>整个支架和橱柜的高度，参考标准为 1950 年代在墨西哥流行一时的传统咖啡馆，人们站在那里一边制作咖啡，边喝边聊天。奶油色的陶瓷咖啡杯也传递出复古气息。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171116203342k12SNczjthdiFCf0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171116203347OdQTps3FKXU5qAoP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171116203356M5EmlCLJOn0figcH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171116203402RplHk40gwMEPVFah.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171116203403x5bCuprjvqwJGUtO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.652707\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2017/11/15/samana-coffee-jose-bermudez-vrokka-fango-studio-furniture-homeware/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Architectural Lighting collection by Astro</h3><p>在 Lux Live 2017 活动上，照明品牌 Astro 推出了建筑 LED 系列灯具，简单而精致，中性色调的几何形状，希望能够为现代建筑提供灵活的照明解决方案，融入背景本身，突出建筑本身的特色。</p><p>Astro 联合创始人 John Fearon 和 James Bassant 说：“我们认为建筑照明比灯具本身更重要。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711162036337grPLTYJxAOmloDb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171116203636s7pOanmlMbDiPQr5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.622250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171116203641k0zoKC9H35YVefja.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.astrolighting.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Astro</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Sustainable Terrazzo Homeware collection by Super Local</h3><p>蓬勃发展的旅游业，为非洲东海岸的热带岛屿桑给巴尔制造了大量废弃玻璃瓶，荷兰设计工作室 Super Local 的两位设计师 Luc van Hoeckel 和 Pim van Baarsen，在 2015 年从桑给巴尔回来后，开始尝试回收这些玻璃瓶，并与桑给巴尔的本土匠人合作，将其转化为水磨石，制成各种家居用品。</p><p>在刚刚结束的荷兰设计周上，Super Local 展示了最新系列的成品，包括长凳、桌子、盘子和花瓶。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171116203753Q0OzXHAynJmMZ7E5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171116203759qBdIOl9Wsb8pEQZo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711162038028L0RwGqkjbSEHCYd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171116203804h2FeXzin46d08y9u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171116203805FOARvT612GWNK3ng.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2017/11/16/super-local-bottle-up-terrazzo-homeware-zanzibar-good-design-bad-world-dutch-design-week/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Turi Wall Clock by Internoitaliano</h3><p>Turi 是意大利设计品牌 Internoitaliano 推出的一款挂钟，简洁的造型充分展示了铜这种材质的美丽。它让人想到传统的意大利厨房，挂在墙上的锅碗瓢盆展示着女主人娴熟的烹饪技巧。而今，设计师找回了这种久违的场景，以挂钟的形式重现，既展示了传统材料的精美，也体现了现代工艺的细腻。售价 118 美元，<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/shop/design/turi-wall-clock-internoitaliano-11-28-2016/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171116203902gzpAwTL2ouU89bQd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171116203903ku0tH3isgoS9vAxG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171116203909sw3PUBDTWYH7qli8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171116203911zUkRXgW1rBAYD3GI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.internoitaliano.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Internoitaliano</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Swing Rocking Chair by Iwona Kosicka Design</h3><p>波兰设计师 Iwona Kosicka 制作了一款舒适特别的椅子 Swing，圆环状的椅子从天花板上悬挂下来，透着俏皮的意味，邀请人们坐上去。它造型极简，适用于各种现代风格装饰的空间，你也可以把它当作秋千来用，或者更特别的玩法是，从中间跳过去，就像练体操那样。不过因为这是一款木制品的缘故，它并不适合安装在户外。售价 1200 美元，<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/shop/design/circle-swing-iwona-kosicka-10-03-2015/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171116204039cVGC0zqrsEpiMXZa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.752000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171116204042XsoHltSkx74ycrhD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.752000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711162040458kZ4ANQKYoxcidRr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171116204048FJfQdwTrMjnyphE0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.752000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171116204050irME0PJhXG3WIfx6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.752000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171116204058C2t1roGq39xSDW0H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.594796\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/shop/design/circle-swing-iwona-kosicka-10-03-2015/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Equilibrium Bookcase by Malagana Design</h3><p>来自哥伦比亚的 Malagana 设计工作室擅长于利用木材设计各种作品，这款平衡书架便是其中之一。天然木皮的独特纹理，赋予了每一个格子不一样的外观，且他们坚持每一款都是纯手工制作。更特别的点在于木格子的构筑方式，看似不经意的各种角度的堆叠，给人一种摇摇欲坠的感觉，造型足够独特。售价 1020 美元，<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/shop/design/equilibrium-bookcase-walnut-malagana-design-09-12-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171116204157sl3jgnIODrUc2Fzh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171116204202HtYq1A9QZ5DeMBiW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171116204205zeEfLavb7pNSVoct.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171116204207ZmJ2EVUn9d7iXeYw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://malaganadesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Malagana Design</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}